20:40.017 --> 20:41.473
Yeah, sí.

20:41.475 --> 20:43.600
[speaks Spanish]

20:46.641 --> 20:48.307
Excuse me.

20:48.309 --> 20:49.764
Thank you.

20:49.766 --> 20:51.515
When you decide to speak English

20:51.517 --> 20:53.764
I'll be over
in the assimilation aisle.

20:53.766 --> 20:56.557
